notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "I suppose where you come from that passes as humor. Just get out of here."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "[Leave]" linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Ikekilled_3N"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Phil o' course. Way it was always gonna be. It don't mean Ike wasn't a good boy, though. Hell no."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I'm sorry to hear about Ike. I'll leave you in peace." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "IkeOwner"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "I hope Ike keeps this company on the right track."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I'm sure he will, farewell Pete. " linkto "done"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_BAD playertext "You've forsaken your own blood. I hope you'll live your last days in torment." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Name"
notes "Name known"
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "[Shakes Hands] Pete Hogg. Owner of this fine fishing establishment. What can I do ya for <PC>?"
      options {
