Node "PhilKilled_3N"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Ike, of course. Boy'll do a good job and he better make sure he does. Honor his brother's memory. It ain't right, though. Ain't right."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I'm sorry about Phil. I'll leave you in peace." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "PhilOwner"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "I always knew I did the right thing. The only sane thing to do is leave your inheritance to your children. Your real children. "
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Damn right, Pete. May your passing be swift and merciful." linkto "done"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I hope Marie will piss on your grave. See you in hell Pete." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "PleadforIke"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
/* Skill checks for node PleadforIke */

      define_skill_check PleadforIke_speechcheck_hard {
      skill_num = 15;
      difficulty_modifier = 10;
      onsuccess => PleadForIke2;
      onfailure => PleadforIkeFailure;
      }

{
NPCText "Ike? Why? He's not my real son. My grandfather's blood does not run through his veins. It would be treason to my kin, you understand. My father's ghost is going to make my afterlife as miserable as this one. Can't let that happen. The company needs a true Hogg to lead it."
      options {
          int=4 linkflags skill_check Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Ike is a good fisherman. He knows the spots, he has patience. He's got experience. Think about it, Ike was born to be a fisherman." linkto "PleadforIke_speechcheck_hard"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Ike just brought back the biggest load of fish in the history of this town. That ought to count for something. " linkto "PleadForIke2"  notes "This one only appears after the \"Greatest Haul Ever\" quest has been completed. Script conditions will be implemented later."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Look, you pathetic old man, when I say Ike's the better candidate, he is. Understand?" linkto "NotAfraid"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "PleadForIke2"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
/* Skill checks for node PleadForIke2 */

      define_skill_check pleadForIke_speechcheck_hard2 {
      skill_num = 15;
      difficulty_modifier = 10;
      onsuccess => PleadForIke3;
      onfailure => PleadforIkeFailure;
      }
      define_skill_check pleadForIke_speechcheck_hard2 {
      skill_num = 15;
      difficulty_modifier = 10;
      onsuccess => PleadForIke3;
      onfailure => PleadforIkeFailure;
      }

{
NPCText "I don't know. Ike's a good lad, he's been my right hand man for a good while now and he's always done a great job. I just... He's not my son. You can put your boots in the oven, but that doesn't make them biscuits."
      options {
          int=4 linkflags skill_check Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "You love him like a son, he loves you like a father. You raised him like a son. What is he to you but a son?" linkto "pleadForIke_speechcheck_hard2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "He's as much your son as Phil is, and a much better candidate to run your company. Phil just botched a deal by committing fraud. Your grandfather wouldn't want a man like that to his old business into the ground. " linkto "PleadForIke3"  notes "This only appears after you completed the \"Sabotage Phil\" quest"
              }
}
Node "PleadForIke3"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Maybe you're right. Heck, Ike even reminds me of dad sometimes. I didn't name him Hogg for nothing. I taught him the works, he does his job the Hogg way. I always thought Phil was too young to take on such a responsibility... I'll tell the boys about my change of plans first thing tomorrow. "
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "You did the right thing, Pete. Good luck. " linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "PleadforIkeFailure"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
/* Skill checks for node PleadforIkeFailure */

      define_skill_check PleadforIke_speechcheck_rebound {
      skill_num = 15;
      difficulty_modifier = 10;
      onsuccess => PleadForIke2;
      onfailure => Angry;
      }

{
NPCText "No. I don't care if Ike was the best fisherman in the world. He's no Hogg and he ain't running no Hogg's business, period. "
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Blood isn't everything. The future of your company is simply in better hands with Ike. " linkto ""  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Looks like you made up your mind. I'm done talking to you. " linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "pleadforPhil"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Yeah. Ike's a good kid, but Phil is a true Hogg. A savvy businessman just like his grandfather. "
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I'm sure he is. It's a good thing you chose your real son. No bond is as strong as the bond of blood. Nice talking to you Pete." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "PleadforSharing"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
/* Skill checks for node PleadforSharing */

      define_skill_check pleadforsharing_speechcheck_hard {
      skill_num = 15;
      difficulty_modifier = 9;
      onsuccess => PleadForSharing2;
      onfailure => PleadforSharingFailure;
      }
      define_skill_check pleadforsharing_initialcheck {
      skill_num = 15;
      difficulty_modifier = 9;
      onsuccess => PleadForSharing2;
      onfailure => PleadforSharingFailure;
      }

{
NPCText "Equal ownership you say? Sails are up but nobody's at the helm in that head of yours, right? Splitting up the business is like tearing it apart. If you cut a good ship in half it will sink, as sure as you get drunk when you drink. "
      options {
          int=4 linkflags skill_check Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "The boys can work together. Phil is an excellent salesman and Ike knows his way around a trawler. Together they have everything it takes to run this business." linkto "pleadforsharing_initialcheck"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I've spoken to both of them. If you don't let them share the company, neither of them is going to take it. That will surely ruin your company. Face it, old man, you have no real choice in this any more. " linkto "PleadforSharingUltimatum"  notes "This option only shows when the boys have agreed on the ultimatum"
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Pete, your sons are trying to kill each other over this company. If you love them, talk to them and let them share this company. Things have gotten out of hand. " linkto "PleadforSharingLove"  notes "This option only shows when both Sabotage quests have been initiated. "
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_BAD playertext "I'll cut you in half if you don't give both kids their rightful share, pissface. " linkto "NotAfraid"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "You're probably right. See you around Pete. [Leave]" linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "PleadForSharing2"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
/* Skill checks for node PleadForSharing2 */

      define_skill_check pleadforsharing_speechcheck_hard {
      skill_num = 15;
      difficulty_modifier = 9;
      onsuccess => PleadforSharingsucces;
      onfailure => PleadforSharingFailure;
      }

{
NPCText "Sure, both kids have their merits. But Philip is my biological son. I reckon Ike can work for him if he wants to. Dividing up the company is going to leave it scattered and powerless in less than two generations, bub. I might as well blow everything we got to hell right now. "
      options {
          int=8 linkflags skill_check Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "How can you be afraid of your grandchildren scattering your assets when you don't even trust your own two sons with sharing it? Phil and Ike complement each other. They're both called Hogg, they'll run it as a family business I'm sure. Let them share it, Pete." linkto "pleadforsharing_reboundcheck"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Maybe you're right. Have it your way, old man." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "PleadforSharingFailure"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
/* Skill checks for node PleadforSharingFailure */

      define_skill_check pleadforsharing_reboundcheck {
      skill_num = 15;
      difficulty_modifier = 9;
      onsuccess => PleadforSharingsucces;
      onfailure => Angry;
      }
      define_skill_check pleadforsharing_reboundcheck {
      skill_num = 15;
      difficulty_modifier = 9;
      onsuccess => PleadforSharingsucces;
      onfailure => Angry;
      }

{
NPCText "I don't want to hear bout it. If you say one more word about having two damn captains on the bridge of one ship I'll kick you out and drink myself to death. "
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Alright, alright. I'm gone. " linkto "done"  notes ""
          int=4 linkflags skill_check Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Who said anything about two captains on one ship? They'll have different tasks, they excel at different things. Use that to your advantage, Pete. Get the best of both worlds." linkto "pleadforsharing_reboundcheck"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "PleadforSharingLove"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "[His alcohol addled features show as much terror as still possible] What? They're trying to kill each other? I never thought..."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "[MORE]" linkto "PleadforSharingLove_2"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "PleadforSharingLove_2"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "This is all wrong. I'll talk to them and let them share it if they want to. If they both die there will be no Hogg left to run it, trueblood or not. Thanks for telling me, <PC>."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "No problem, Pete. I hope things work out." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "PleadforSharingsucces"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "[Pete smiles showing yellow, crooked teeth] You know what? You're right. Philip has his grandfather's keen nose for business and Ike reminds me of my own dad sometimes, he always knows where the catch is at. Hell I love them both, might as well trust them both. Thanks for showing me what familly's all about, <PC>."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I'm glad you made your decision, Pete. See you around. " linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "PleadforSharingUltimatum"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "[Pete looks angry] They said what? Brats. You raise them, you love them. You care for them and their mother. And then they turn on you, the weasels. Well, obviously they ain't having no problems with taking decisions without old Pete. No reason to stick around scratching my butt, is there? I'm off to the Cutty Sark. Damn those kids, damn them to hell. "
      options {
          int=4 linkflags skill_check Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Wait, Pete. Their plan is very reasonable. The boys can work together. Phil is an excellent salesman and Ike knows his way around a trawler. Together they have everything it takes to run this business." linkto "pleadforsharing_initialcheck"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Yeah, you do that, Pete. Have a drink, you deserve it. See you around." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Quest1"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "So, you been talking to my son?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Yeah. I think Ike should be running the company." linkto "PleadforIke"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I have. Phil is the man for the job. You're doing the right thing Pete. " linkto "pleadforPhil"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Sure have. Both of them. I think the company would be suited best if the brothers had equal ownership and worked together. " linkto "PleadforSharing"  notes "This is available only when the player has convinced the brothers to work together. "
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I don't want to get involved. Good luck old man." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
