}
Node "SharedOwnership"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "[Pete smiles] My sons told me they were both, whatchamacallit? Chairmen. It ain't really the Hogg way, two men doing the job of one. But whatever, they seem to be doing a good job. I guess I can die with a satisfied mind now. Thanks for your help, <PC>. "
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "No problem, Pete. I hope your last few days will be pleasant." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Story"
notes "This smooths out Pete for the speech solution to this quest."
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "[Sighs] Well, you seem like a trustworthy person, <PC>. Have a drink and I'll tell you. "
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Always up for a drink. Tell me your story, Pete." linkto "Story2_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_BAD playertext "No thanks, but I will hear your story." linkto "Angry"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Story2_1"
notes "Put the effects of a bottle of beer on the PC (-1 Per for a while) as a result of accepting the drink."
is_wtg = false
/* Skill checks for node Story2_1 */

      define_skill_check Speech_Check_harder {
      skill_num = 15;
      difficulty_modifier = -7;
      onsuccess => Nomoredrinking;
      onfailure => Angry;
      }

{
NPCText "Good! Always nice to meet a fellow drinker. I'll be frank with ya, <PC>: I'm dying. Medicine woman says my drinking habits are bitin' me in the ass. Mighty whale of a liver's turned into a pathetic little shrimp."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "[MORE]" linkto "Story2_2"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Story2_2"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "I tell ya son, that's tough news to swallow for a hard working man. I thought I was gonna live forever. That I was one of them folks who sail to the other shore with their ship intact. Want another drink?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Yeah, go on." linkto "Story3"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_BAD playertext "No, I've had enough. So have you, Pete, I don't need your shrivelled liver to give up on you during our conversation." linkto "Speech_Check_harder"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Story3"
notes "Put the effects of (another) bottle of beer on the PC (-1 Per for a while) as a result of accepting the drink."
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "[Coughs heavily] When my pappy died he left me this company. I worked as hard as he did turning it into what it is now. I don't have no regrets, you know. My Marie will be the wealthiest widow in town. All I'm worried about is my business. My sons do a fine job working for me, but when Phil inherits the company he'd better run a tight ship.  "
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Why Phil? You said you had more than one son. " linkto "Story4"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Yeah. Guess you're right. Nice talking to you, Pete. [Leave]" linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Story4"
notes "Gets the Fisherman Family Feud quest\n"
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "I did? Well, you see. Phil is my only real son. Ike is Marie's kid, I raised him like my own and hell, I guess I love him like my own. But he sure ain't no Hogg. I don't know how he's taking it though. Maybe you can talk to him for me, he's been all cold with me since I told him about the adoption. "
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I'll see what I can do." linkto "done"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I don't want to get involved in your messy family affairs, old man. Have a nice death. " linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Troubled"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
/* Skill checks for node Troubled */

      define_skill_check Speech_check_easy {
      skill_num = 15;
      difficulty_modifier = -4;
      onsuccess => Story;
      onfailure => Angry;
      }

{
NPCText "Troubled? I'm just feeling a little under the weather, 's all. Now state your business or get lost. "
      options {
          int=4 linkflags skill_check Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Then it's gotta be raining dog piss. What's your story?" linkto "Speech_check_easy"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Very well. Something else then." linkto "Greetingknown"  notes ""
              }
}
